data.description: This lovely 3 bed / 2.5 bath offers a great space for the family in San Juan. This property is located near many great schools and parks that are perfect for the kids while also having quick access to the expressway. Feel welcomed into the main living area with high ceilings and an open concept into the dining area. In the kitchen is a dark island for more counter or bar space as well as a pantry for all your storage needs. The primary bedroom is downstairs, along with a laundry room and half bath. Upstairs is another living area that can be used as an office area, gym area or even a game room. In the backyard is a covered patio and spacious yard with an extra area to the side of the home for dogs or other pets! Please note A/C is only two years old, and home also has newer roof.   **Selling as is.
